snippet.title: YARG Setlist: Wave 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
It's here!! Wave 1 of the official YARG setlist has arrived bringing with it 5 new songs featuring Portraits of Tracy, bottom bunk, KINGSEEKER, Stone Deep and Höwler! This is just the beginning y'all, we can't wait to show more in the VERY near future!

Download the YARG launcher here!: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARG/releases

In order to get these songs in-game, just click "YARG Setlist" in the launcher and then hit the install button.

If you're a developer, artist, or band and are interested in contributing to YARG, feel free to join us on Discord, GitHub, or contact us via our email. We are 100% open source and always welcome anyone who wants to contribute!

Interested in getting your music added to the official YARG setlist or a DLC pack? Reach out to yargchartingteam@gmail.com and we'll get back to you as soon as possible!
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Website: https://yarg.in/ 
Discord: https://discord.gg/sqpu4R552r
GitHub: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARG







don't eat the gems
